headline: Arthur J. Gallagher & Co. To Webcast Investor Meeting With Management
summary: Arthur J. Gallagher & Co. will be hosting an informal management meeting with the investment community in New York City on Tuesday, December 16th from 8:30 am until approximately 11:30 am ET. During the meeting, the company's operating and financial leaders will present background information and commentary on the company's business operations and financial outlook, and will also take questions from in-person attendees. The agenda will be available a week in advance at www.ajg.com/irmeeting.

headline: Arthur J. Gallagher buys UK’s First Actuarial
summary: First Actuarial will operate under the guidance of Arthur UK Benefits and HR Consulting Division head David Piltz.
